OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex met
OL,7,Fsurvivors of the Bondi Beach terror
OL,8,Fattack after the couple arrived in
OL,9,FSydney on the last day of their
OL,10,FAustralia visit.
OL,12,FHarry and Meghan also met emergency
OL,13,Fworkers who responded to last year's
OL,14,Fterror attack against the Jewish
OL,15,Fcommunity, as well as representatives
OL,16,Fof the Sydney Jewish Museum, which is
OL,17,Fopening an exhibition on the attacks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
