OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776459559
OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,FAfter arriving at the Bondi Surf
OL,7,FBathers' Life Saving Club on Friday
OL,8,Fmorning, the couple spoke to Jessica
OL,9,FChapnik Khan, who survived the attack
OL,10,Fwhile shielding her five-year-old
OL,11,Fdaughter after attending a Hanukkah
OL,12,Fparty.
OL,14,FMs Chapnik Khan said it was an
OL,15,F"honour" to meet the couple, adding:
OL,16,F"The greater problem in the world
OL,17,Fright now is hate.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@HO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776459559
OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,F"Hate is a human problem that we're
OL,7,Ffacing, a very big problem. So to
OL,8,Fhighlight that, to be able to connect
OL,9,Fwith them on this heart level, I think
OL,10,Fis very special."
OL,12,FMs Chapnik Khan told the Press
OL,13,FAssociation: "When the gunshots
OL,14,Fstarted, we started running towards
OL,15,Fthe beach, and it became very clear we
OL,16,Fweren't going to make it to the beach
OL,17,Fand stay alive. So we hid in a picnic
OL,18,Farea.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]uD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776459559
OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,F"I didn't want my daughter to die with
OL,7,Fgunshots and sirens and wailing
OL,8,Fmothers ` I just couldn't reconcile
OL,9,Fthat those would be her last moments.
OL,11,F"So I spoke really clearly into her
OL,12,Fear, and I said: 'My darling, go
OL,13,Finside yourself where all the love is,
OL,14,Fand stay there. Stay in your heart, my
OL,15,Fbaby'.
OL,17,F"And she heard me, and we laid there
OL,18,Ftogether in this heart space in the
OL,19,Fmiddle of horror for who knows how
OL,20,Flong, and we survived."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
