CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776459559
OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,FThe couple also spoke to Elon Zizer,
OL,7,F40, who survived after being shot
OL,8,Fnumerous times while shielding his
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's an honour to meet the
OL,12,Fduke and duchess. It's very beautiful
OL,13,Fthat they've come and made an effort
OL,14,Fto meet us.
OL,16,F"It's very special ` it makes us feel
OL,17,Fheard."
OL,26,@sD@JOUxD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
