OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,FHarry and Meghan examined artefacts
OL,7,Fthat will make up the new exhibition
OL,8,Fat the Sydney Jewish Museum, including
OL,9,Fwell-wishing messages and
OL,10,Fillustrations of members of the public
OL,11,Fwho were hailed as heroes for helping
OL,12,Fpeople during the attack.
OL,14,FThe couple met Shannon Biederman, the
OL,15,Fmuseum's senior curator, who said it
OL,16,Fwas "really special" to have them
OL,17,Fvisit.
OL,26,@xD@EOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
