OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,FFifteen people died and dozens more
OL,7,Fwere injured when gunmen opened fire
OL,8,Fon a crowd of more than 1,000
OL,9,Fcelebrating Hanukkah in Bondi's Archer
OL,10,FPark on December 14.
OL,12,FNaveed Akram, 24, is accused of 15
OL,13,Fcounts of murder and one count of
OL,14,Fcommitting a terrorist act over the
OL,15,Fattack in which dozens of people were
OL,16,Finjured at Sydney's Archer Park in
OL,17,FDecember.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776459559
OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,FNew South Wales Police allege Akram
OL,7,Fand his father ` Sajid, 50, who was
OL,8,Fshot dead by police at the scene `
OL,9,Fcarried out Australia's worst mass
OL,10,Fshooting since 1996, targeting the
OL,11,FJewish festival of lights.
OL,13,FWhile in Sydney, the duke and duchess
OL,14,Fwill also join members of the Invictus
OL,15,FGames community on the water of the
OL,16,Fcity's famous harbour and meet past
OL,17,Fcompetitors.
OL,19,FMeghan will also be interviewed on
OL,20,Fstage at a "girls' weekend" retreat,
OL,21,Fcosting #1,400 per ticket.
OL,26,@|D@LOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
