OL,3,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex meet Bondi
OL,4,CBeach terror attack survivors
OL,6,FVIP tickets for the event at the five-
OL,7,Fstar InterContinental Coogee Beach
OL,8,Fhotel cost #1,670 and include a group
OL,9,Ftable photo with the duchess.
OL,11,FHer appearance was announced last
OL,12,Fmonth by Gemma O'Neill, host of the
OL,13,FHer Best Life podcast, which is
OL,14,Forganising the 300-person event.
OL,16,FThe visit will conclude at a rugby
OL,17,Ffixture in Sydney between New South
OL,18,FWales Waratahs and Moana Pasifika at
OL,19,Fthe Allianz Stadium on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
